Author: Birdie49
Text: When I was at a healthy weight, I was insatiable. Now I'm underweight and one of the symptoms of malnutrition that I'm experiencing is a lowered sex drive and honestly? It's a relief. My current partner's libido is much lower than mine used to be, but since my ED has lowered it, we just about match. It's definitely a considerable reason that I don't want to recover -- I worry that me having such a high sex drive again would be frustrating and stressful for both of us.
